{"tid":1760164,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「困局解法」再唔入黎推香港人就全撚部一齊食屎","createTime":"2019-11-28T04:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T13:28:35.000Z","uid":107157,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8358a4a6bec7438aa4d75852af9c669e58618677","tid":1760164,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:33:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「食左你隻卒就當贏」</div><br />\n<br />\n經過左人權法案同埋區選後，香港人就好似喪失左目標咁，係咁開party，冇左回事，革命之火係咁減少。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「棵菜你平左5毫比我就算啦」</div><br />\n<br />\n而一個軍人打贏一場仗之後係並唔會開P慶祝，而係會乘勝追擊，而呢點香港人完全做唔到。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「香港人需要一個新目標」</div><br />\n<br />\n而依家既香港人正正就需要一個新目標，而且係更加具威脅性既新目標。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「追究警暴，追究官暴」</div><br />\n<br />\n警暴問題已經唔係第一日既事，我地都已經追究左好耐。但係大家忽略左高官既暴政，一樣害撚死好多人，大家應該連同高官一齊追究。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「人權法一過，高官無退路可走」</div><br />\n<br />\n班死人高官一有事就潛水去外國，家陣佢地已經冇晒退路，子女可能係外國做肉蔘，令佢地寸步難行，香港人應該乘勝追擊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最後</span></span>懇請大家改改口號:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">五大要求，缺一不可</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"ccd06aa20fc9d74fdaf2ca89a410be71b8ea2482","tid":1760164,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:39:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"857230b3e6cf5ffece5dd8a39b4261e608fac672","tid":1760164,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:40:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"202e2eab4ae0b4048642a300033188580c1e1f0e","tid":1760164,"uid":114122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:41:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69360bc730ce8dc77cf73f061a75a8004cc4a465","tid":1760164,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:43:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfe536a2d118802d2c08f77566b8d2935af63b16","tid":1760164,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:43:26.000Z","msg":"支持追究背後果班撚樣<br />\n<br />\n唔係有佢哋響背後在明在暗嘅支持，班冚家剷點夠膽咁猖狂？"},{"pid":"730ed4fa94df69547a9a4c9a3ae149dcc2f800b0","tid":1760164,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfe536a2d118802d2c08f77566b8d2935af63b16","tid":1760164,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:43:26.000Z","msg":"支持追究背後果班撚樣<br />\n<br />\n唔係有佢哋響背後在明在暗嘅支持，班冚家剷點夠膽咁猖狂？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:45:36.000Z","msg":"遂步狙擊先，要遂部機破。<br />\n幕後黑手係支共，你知我知單眼佬都知，<br />\n但係對付支共仲未係時候"},{"pid":"4f17503859d5ea4e6f700b4a53b7e6e5872b75d9","tid":1760164,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:46:31.000Z","msg":"等港豬放工我再推過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae71e2ada7c0fb568d3012ce6fbda23362c0716","tid":1760164,"uid":290611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:50:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"897bb4d71a957b0b47ee738b270612c6210b7166","tid":1760164,"uid":206705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:51:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68decabada1b83a4e52601bda28f561c07fc8164","tid":1760164,"uid":290611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:53:26.000Z","msg":"可以講係叫大家乘勝追擊 不過唔建議每次都道德綁架叫人唔升級就係港豬 明白樓主是好意提醒香港人要時刻保持警覺 不過也要有計劃從長計議 先唔會泄左道氣"},{"pid":"fc0eebfa20ef2e1b8bf6b133e44c3e63061b4c19","tid":1760164,"uid":276548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1625000/1625343/cycn20170116053_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1625000%2F1625343%2Fcycn20170116053_1024_1024.jpg&h=c7153407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柒婆我有時真係忍唔住笑<br />\n到頭來港豬原來就想走番回頭路<br />\n幻想用議會制衡到港共<br />\n用多十年時間慢慢玩吧<br />\n最後你地一再會發覺今日想法ON9<br />\n今日當SAVE POINT<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65315327954d57cc1399ee0feb439561eee9a183","tid":1760164,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T05:49:35.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc2af4fccc80f8127eef33bdfc9035c29c3fed8","tid":1760164,"uid":91205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T05:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2b923dc263f3f7ca4857775f08dda05a9ed7ce","tid":1760164,"uid":91205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T13:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}